Jalopy Maven Plugin

 The Jalopy Maven Plugin formats java source files following a coding convention.

* Goals Overview

   The Jalopy Plugin has one goal:

   * {{{format-mojo.html}jalopy:format}} Format the java source files following a coding convention.

